messages.message:
I'm super psyched about helping create release notes for our 2020.03.16 - Release. I need your help to get some traction on release notes. Yes, you. If you contributed a feature, bug fix, or change to Instabase that we want our users to know about, use the Release Notes field in the Jira. (If multiple Jiras cover the same feature, pick the epic or relevant Jira). Read all about release notes at Instabase (https://instabase.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/DOCS/pages/185696404/Release+notes).
I'm here for us all! Ask me questions.
Tagging tech leads for greater visibility: @Kerry @dlluncor @Heymian @shaunak @Ashish @lydia <!subteam^SQC4GLFN2>
